{"tid":559752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大埔翻巴士】25歲女扮家屬「發死人財」 涉募捐行騙落網","createTime":"2018-02-13T12:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T19:47:44.000Z","uid":150685,"like":305,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"46f073fca514ba36274fe055fbc49b7821bcae98","tid":559752,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180213/large/1518521027_12ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180213%2Flarge%2F1518521027_12ae.jpg&h=c5502694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔公路翻九巴大車禍造成19人死亡慘劇，全城悲慟，惟近日有人在網上發帖子招遙撞騙，自稱是死者家屬，更列出兩個銀行戶口，呼籲網民捐款。警方經調查後，在旺角拘捕一名25歲女子，她涉嫌有犯罪或不誠實意圖取用電腦，警方稍後交代案件。<br />\n<br />\n涉事帖子在網上社交群組瘋傳，發帖者聲稱「尋好心人」，在今次大埔翻巴士大車禍中，其姑奶「失去了經濟支柱，遺下一對十個月的孖仔」，「希望大家可以略盡綿力，讓我姑奶家人會好過點及重新振作起來」。<br />\n<br />\n發帖者又列出兩個銀行戶口號碼，指自己會「暫代收款」，並會將全數款項交給遺孀，並「感謝各位有心人」。不過有精明的網民已即時質疑有人「發死人財」，怒斥「搵食行遠啲」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180213/57829861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180213%2F57829861&d=juZNQ8TWd%2FZKTWwpyWEy8jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=314869da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180213%2F57829861&h=23e43be2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180213/57829861</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好仆街"},{"pid":"85e88fd512a615bfbd8927904cd3774a766eb1e1","tid":559752,"uid":810,"like":225,"dislike":3,"score":222,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"撞正呀爺交緊戲都敢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7965961ef26087f2155d1fea74058f832a3e742","tid":559752,"uid":106375,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:45